YASMon NEWS File

See README for more information about YASMon.


===========================

Version 0.1.0 (June 18, 2010)

 * Fullscreen view
 * Added history view
 * Added filesystem usage view


============================

Version 0.0.5 (May 27, 2010)

 * Added static meta-info view in remote and local


============================

Version 0.0.4 (May 25, 2010)

 * Added unit testing
 * Improved error handling
 * Increased python 3 compatibility
   * Removed integer division
 * Fixed race condition on GUI exit


============================

Version 0.0.3 (May 23, 2010)

 * Fixed various UI display bugs in Qt4 interface
 * Remote memory and processor usage monitoring


============================

Version 0.0.2 (May 22, 2010)

 * Added YASMond startup script
 * Remote uptime viewing
 * Improved error handling


============================

Version 0.0.1 (May 21, 2010)

 * Initial version
 * Local CPU, RAM, and uptime monitoring

